@host = http://localhost:5000

### Health check
GET {{host}}/

### Create a trade
# @name createTrade
POST {{host}}/api/trades
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "instrument": "USDCAD",
  "quantity": 1000000,
  "side": "Buy"
}

### Fetch the trade we just created
GET {{host}}/api/trades/{{createTrade.response.body.id}}

### Creating with a non-positive quantity should 400
POST {{host}}/api/trades
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "instrument": "USDCAD",
  "quantity": 0,
  "side": "Buy"
}

### Fetching an unknown id should 404
GET {{host}}/api/trades/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
